rows.label: tlk47100042_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Well! Never in a million years did I
think that I would meet the true heroes
here! It is such an honor to meet you!

rows.label: tlk47100042_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Ever since your heroic deeds, Phonex have
started leaving their territory to explore,
so word has started to travel!

rows.label: tlk47100042_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I'd like to travel to
places like Liberalitas
and Gula myself someday...
